  "translations": {
    "en": "Abu Ja'far Muhammad ibn Ali ibn al-Husayn ibn Musa ibn Babawayh al-Qummi (may Allah be pleased with him) narrated to us. He said: Hamza ibn Muhammad ibn Ahmad ibn Ja'far ibn Muhammad ibn Zayd ibn Ali ibn al-Husayn ibn Ali ibn Abi Talib (peace be upon them) narrated to us. He said: Abu Abdillah Abd al-Aziz ibn Muhammad ibn Isa al-Abhari narrated to me. He said: Abu Abdillah Muhammad ibn Zakariyya al-Jawhari al-Ghilabi al-Basri narrated to us. He said: Shu'ayb ibn Waqid narrated to us. He said: Al-Husayn ibn Yazid narrated to us from al-Sadiq Ja'far ibn Muhammad, from his father, from his forefathers, from Amir al-Mu'minin Ali ibn Abi Talib (peace be upon them), who said:",
